{"tid":1947185,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2019.3.31 抗戰起點 （WSJ 記憶特緝）","createTime":"2020-03-28T06:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T06:11:53.000Z","uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33e7e4748291b77aaff9ce538f4b3aaacc161bda","tid":1947185,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">終於</span>係2019<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">放棄對中共、港共政權所有信任</span></strong>。反送中由政權在二月，以20日極短、橫蠻、粗暴的假資詢方式將送中條例帶入議會。<br />\n是赤裸裸的強姦民意 - 令人民意識到香港政府正式失去「義」。<br />\n<br />\n該方法直接引發 2019年3月31日嘅第一次反送中遊行，為香港人對抗極權的戰爭揭起序幕。<br />\n繼後，政權繼續莫視4月28日的第二次反送中13萬人遊行亦令香港各界自始之後開始發聲。之後五月尾由<strong><ins>第一個由香港人自發</ins></strong>(派傳單)行動，<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">兩星期無間斷地氈式文宣</span></strong>及6月6日法律界的靜默遊行，亦激起香港人對反送中事宜嘅緊急性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/44ced6/f/800x0/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20190605/720pix/1559750142_2f09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F44ced6%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20190605%2F720pix%2F1559750142_2f09.png&h=42770ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而6月9日100萬人上街示威起直到今日嘅抗爭行動亦令香港人及世界目不遐吸，令自由社會反思對抗極權需要的堅持及犧牲。和、勇、仁、義係香港人抗爭的必需品，為保持抗爭行動的正當性及持續性的原料，令香港人發揮團結一致守望相助的精神，以上原素缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tufv4Zpm0JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTufv4Zpm0JU&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=4691151a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tufv4Zpm0JU</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然面對疫情及港共政權的打壓，各區連儂牆、良心經濟圈的建立鞏固了抗爭的基礎。因此，政權<strong><ins>極力灠捕連儂牆手足</ins></strong>，以衛生條例打壓中小型黃店 (藍店乞食中，四人餐桌對佢地無影響)。<br />\n<br />\n以上係睇完條片之後少少感受，面對極權我地要時刻警惕。希望香港人繼續團結，締造香港魂，繼續對抗極權。直至五大訴求達到，在煲底下除罩相認為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">P.S.</span><br />\nCap 599其實惡過緊急法<br />\n<br />\n資源來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/連登仔的成就解鎖/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E8%A7%A3%E9%8E%96%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=d8696989\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E8%A7%A3%E9%8E%96%2F&h=b18b4479\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/連登仔的成就解鎖/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/陳祖為回望-1981-年的自己-點解我會問個咁-sharp-嘅問題/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%99%B3%E7%A5%96%E7%82%BA%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%9B-1981-%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%88%91%E6%9C%83%E5%95%8F%E5%80%8B%E5%92%81-sharp-%E5%98%85%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0ZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=8e2d35bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%99%B3%E7%A5%96%E7%82%BA%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%9B-1981-%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%88%91%E6%9C%83%E5%95%8F%E5%80%8B%E5%92%81-sharp-%E5%98%85%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%2F&h=45a718b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/陳祖為回望-1981-年的自己-點解我會問個咁-sharp-嘅問題/</a>"},{"pid":"da17310d4bb209cc16333313e468c924fdaef4c1","tid":1947185,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe4bc45c8e2da72fb110dd7920ab5fc0c26eac4a","tid":1947185,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}